text: Admetula vossi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The maximum shell size is 13 mm ==Distribution== This species is found along the Bahamas. ==References== * Petit, R.E. & Harasewych, M.G. (2005) Catalogue of the superfamily Cancellarioidea Forbes and Hanley, 1851 (Gastropoda: Prosobranchia)- 2nd edition. Zootaxa, 1102, 3-161. NIZT 682 ==External links== * Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1976
title: Admetula vossi
